sourcesContent: import React from 'react'; import { Button } from '@mui/material'; const Staff = ({ staff, index }) => { return ( {index} {staff.name} {staff.surname} {staff.asma} {staff.unit} {staff.rank} {staff.specialization} {staff.display_name} {staff.mobile_phone} {staff.work_phone} {staff.position_of_responsibility} {staff.special_category} {staff.indefinitely} {staff.mta_payment} ) } export default Staff;
